    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13340#discussion_r3229235290\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>We could also split out the logic for checking whether mpk is available to like <code>wasmtime-internal-core</code> or something so that we could build a binary that exits 0/1 in minimal time but still ensure that this check in CI never differs from the check we use in wasmtime itself at some point in the future.</p>\n</blockquote>",
