        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> tschneidereit created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13340#discussion_r3229318291\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>so a tiny crate that we use in wasmtime, and also in a test binary that doesn't have any other dependencies? That makes sense to me.</p>\n</blockquote>",
