    {
        "content": "<p>tschneidereit <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13340#issuecomment-4434233720\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13340\">PR #13340</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Will apply Nick's suggestions—probably tomorrow—but this seems to have very nice results: CI runs for PR checks went from between 14 and 17 minutes to below 10. I'll trigger a full run with the next commit to see what that looks like as well.</p>\n</blockquote>",
